OL,4,Cwith colleague walks free from court
OL,6,FAn "obsessed" former police constable
OL,7,Fconvicted of stalking his estranged
OL,8,Fpolicewoman wife who he caught having
OL,9,Fsex with a colleague has walked free
OL,10,Ffrom court.
OL,12,FGavin Harper, 45, discovered the
OL,13,Flovers in a Screwfix car park in
OL,14,FBirkenhead, Merseyside, after he
OL,15,Fsecretly placed a tracker device on
OL,16,Fthe underside of Stephanie Glynn's
OL,17,Fvehicle.
