OL,4,Cwith colleague walks free from court
OL,6,FMerseyside Police officers Ms Glynn,
OL,7,F40, and Inspector Andrew McLullich,
OL,8,F42, were naked from the waist down in
OL,9,Fthe back of the latter's car when
OL,10,FHarper crept up and filmed them at the
OL,11,Fwindow with his mobile phone.
OL,13,FProsecutors said it was the
OL,14,Fculmination of a campaign of
OL,15,F"obsessive, intrusive and unwanted
OL,16,Fbehaviour" against Ms Glynn from
OL,17,FDecember 2020 to February 2021.
