OL,6,FLast month a jury at Liverpool Crown
OL,7,FCourt found the father-of-two guilty
OL,8,Fof aggravated stalking which included
OL,9,Fsecretly bugging Ms Glynn's car,
OL,10,Flistening to her conservations,
OL,11,Ftracking her whereabouts and taking
OL,12,Fher phone without her permission.
OL,14,FThe defendant and Ms Glynn met as
OL,15,FMerseyside Police officers and were in
OL,16,Fa six-year relationship before they
OL,17,Fmarried in 2018.
