OL,6,FBut Ms Glynn left the family home in
OL,7,FDecember 2020 after she grew close to
OL,8,Fher work mentor Mr McLullich, an
OL,9,Facting inspector at the time and
OL,10,Fformerly her supervising sergeant.
OL,12,FGiving evidence, Harper said he wanted
OL,13,F"undeniable proof" of the affair which
OL,14,Fhe said Ms Glynn had persistently
OL,15,Fdenied.
OL,17,FHis intention was to pass the video to
OL,18,Fpolice as evidence of two serving
OL,19,Fofficers having an inappropriate
OL,20,Frelationship during Covid lockdown
OL,21,Frestrictions, he said.
