OL,6,FOn Monday, 29 April, Judge David
OL,7,FPotter sentenced Harper to two years
OL,8,Fin jail, suspended for two years.
OL,10,FThe judge told him he would have faced
OL,11,Fimmediate custody but for the
OL,12,Fsignificant effect that imprisonment
OL,13,Fwould have had on Harper's elderly
OL,14,Fparents and youngest son.
