OL,6,FBut he said their acts were "made
OL,7,Fworse" by Harper filming them on his
OL,8,Fmobile phone.
OL,10,FHe said: "It was a further gross
OL,11,Fexample of stalking designed to
OL,12,Fmaximise their humiliation to your
OL,13,Fadvantage. Your conduct was intended
OL,14,Fto maximise fear or distress. You
OL,15,Fresorted to stalking out of a sense of
